<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #007bff;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to Enhanced AI Agent!</h1>
    </div>
    <p>Hello {{username}},</p>
    <p>Thank you for joining Enhanced AI Agent. We're excited to have you on board!</p>
    <p>Here are a few things you can do to get started:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Create your first AI prompt</li>
      <li>Explore our prompt templates</li>
      <li>Configure your preferences</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      <a href="{{verificationLink}}" class="button">Verify Your Email</a>
    </p>
    <p>If you have any questions, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
    <p>Best regards,<br>The Enhanced AI Agent Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 